('40385','14394','5','Unique horse ranch on a plot of 67.533m², near Palma de Mallorca'),
('40386','14395','5','This exclusive horse ranch in Mediterranean-style was finished in 2001 and sits on a large plot of 67.533 m².\r\nThe property was constructed to a very high standard using the latest technology and top-quality materials. The property with a gross floor area of 1.579 m², consists of the main house, an indoor pool with sauna, horse stables and agricultural wing, guest rooms and accommodation for staff, 3 garages plus 3 carports and more than 20 parking lots for guests, two beautiful inner courtyards, covered arcades, several outbuildings, an old finca for agricultural equipment and various riding arenas.\r\n\r\nThe living house has full cellar and can be also accessed via lift. Here you will find e.g. a wine cellar, wine bar with arcades, floor heating and air conditioning, kitchen alcove, cold store and the staircase.\r\nVia the beautiful patio you will reach the living area located on the ground floor.\r\nFrom the entrance hall supported by columns you will enter the spacious living room with bar, a library with marble chimney, dining room, followed by the fireplace room (breakfast room), guest bedroom with bathroom en suite, guest toilet, laundry room with second entrance and an open-plan kitchen of the highest comfort level. All rooms are equipped with stone carvings and ceilings with wooden beams.\r\nThe gallery, decorated with coffered ceiling and situated on the upper floor, leads to the three master suites. All suites offer enough space for a wardrobe.\r\nThe guest wing disposes of a 2 bedroom apartment and 2 further rooms for 2 additional guest apartments with bathroom and kitchenette. All connections are pre-installed.\r\nThe building services are controlled by a central computer system.\r\n\r\nThe outbuilding comprises of a spacious wellness area with a 8x5m swimming pool with counter current system, picture windows, Jacuzzi, Finnish - and Turkish sauna, cloakroom, bathroom, gym and shower.\r\nThe beautiful laid-out exterior area offers an artificial lake of 444m² with water fountains, olive trees, almond trees, flower beds, fields , a 40x20m iluminated horse riding and jumping arena, a dressage riding arena with the Olympic measures of 20x60m, 5 separate paddocks with direct access from the stables, eventing course with natural obstacles and water basins.\r\nFurthermore there are riding and walking trails on the property. All fields are irrigated by two deep wells, with 40,000 hours per liter. All irrigation systems are connected.\r\nThis is an unique property for horse lovers searching for a horse ranch of highest quality on Mallorca. If you would like to have more information about the property, please send us an email with your postal address and a landline number and we will contact you directly.'),
